    <main class="container">
        <section>
            <h2>Privacy Policy - Venue and Event Bookings</h2>
           

            <p>At EventEase Management, we value your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our venue and event booking services. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring a smooth booking process while not collecting personal information beyond what is necessary.</p>

            <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
            <p>We do not collect personal information such as your name, email, or phone number. However, when booking venues or events, we collect basic data related to your booking, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Venue Information:</strong> The name of the venue, venue type, and the dates the venue is booked for.</li>
                <li><strong>Event Information:</strong> Details about the event being booked, including event name, event type, and event dates.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>2. How We Use the Information</h3>
            <p>The information we collect is used solely for the purpose of managing venue and event bookings:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Booking Management:</strong> To ensure the venue is booked correctly, we track venue availability and event scheduling.</li>
                <li><strong>Availability and Conflict Resolution:</strong> To ensure there are no double bookings or scheduling conflicts.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>3. How We Share the Information</h3>
            <p>We do not share your booking data with third parties, except as follows:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> We may share venue and event booking data with trusted service providers who assist in maintaining our booking system or hosting our platform, but they will not use your data for other purposes.</li>
                <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> If required by law, we may disclose booking information to comply with legal obligations.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>4. Contact Us</h3>
            <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
            <p><strong>EventEase Management</strong></p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@eventease.com">support@eventease.com</a></p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 EventEase Booking System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
